==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Abstemiousness
<hw>Ab*ste"mi*ous*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of being
abstemious, temperate, or sparing in the use of food and strong drinks.
It expresses a greater degree of abstinence than
<xex>temperance</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Abstention</ent>⟦br⟧
